g.text: SCENARIO 1 — Trip → Open → Half-Open → Closed (Probe Success)
SCENARIO 2 — Half-Open Probe FAILS → Back to OPEN
── Still OPEN — requests continue to be rejected ──
mu.Lock() → OPEN, timeout not elapsed → mu.Unlock()

text.tspan: CLOSED → OPEN: failures >= maxFailures(5) within failureWindow(10s)
HALF_OPEN → CLOSED: upstream() returns nil (probe success)
HALF_OPEN → OPEN: upstream() returns error (probe failure)
failures field: incremented on 5xx, reset to 0 on success in CLOSED
lastFailureTime: time.Time, written on every failure (all states)
windowStart: reset when entering OPEN state
